  "body": "While testing [helm-diff](https://github.com/databus23/helm-diff) with helm-3.0.0-beta.3, I found that there's a regression - it is missing the fix for #4170.\r\n\r\n`helm-diff` needs to return 1 on errors and 2 on changes detected. helm 2.x had also been returning 1 for all the non-zero exit codes from plugins but it was fixed via #4367.\r\n\r\nI've confirmed that it isn't fixed for helm v3 and reading code from the `dev-v3` branch I've also confirmed that it misses changes from #4367.\r\n\r\nCan we just cherry-pick the fix into the helm3 dev branch?\r\n\r\n---\r\n\r\nOutput of `helm version`:\r\n\r\n```\r\nversion.BuildInfo{Version:\"v3.0.0-beta.3\", GitCommit:\"5cb923eecbe80d1ad76399aee234717c11931d9a\", GitTreeState:\"clean\", GoVersion:\"go1.12.9\"}\r\n```\r\n\r\n\r\n",
